cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.HC 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, for classification of Alzheimer's disease using fMRI data. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of these techniques for medical diagnosis also falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
